# Project Euler 2: Even Fibonacci Numbers
# Each new Fibonacci term is generated by adding the previous two. Find the
# sum of all even-valued terms not exceeding four million.
# Answer: 4613732

a = 1
b = 2
total = 0
while a <= 4000000
    if a % 2 == 0
        total = total + a
    end
    next_val = a + b
    a = b
    b = next_val
end

print total
